Job Description:
Brief Job Description:    
Create, analyze and control the achievement of the MBO and the effectiveness of Sales activity;
Build a good relationship with potential customer and do sales marketing job include follow up new project;
Do HORENSO (Reporting, Communication, and Discussion) to superior;
Developing a business development strategy focused on volume and profit gain;
Conduct high-level industry research to identify new market, customer needs and monitor competitor activities to develop effective sales;
Promote Idemitsu's products/services addressing customer objectives/requirements.
 General Requirement:    
Have a Bachelor Degree majoring in Sales & Marketing and Business Development;
Excellent English in written and verbal communication, Japanese and Chinese/Mandarin is welcome;
Excellent in analytical, technical, communication, negotiation, planning, and presentation skill;
Excellent in planning and time management;
Able to critical thinking;
Proven working experience in customer support, data analyst, business development and sales marketing;
Familiar with all Microsoft Office (Word, Excel and Power Point);
Have a valid Driving License (SIM A).
 Specific Requirement:
Have 5 years working experience Sales & Marketing (Preferable Industrial Lubricant);
Proven working experience in customer support, data analyst, business development and sales marketing;
Have good market knowledge, sales and marketing.
Have good knowledge about Business and Project Management;
Willing to conduct business trip;
Willing to work at Kawasan Industri GIIC Cikarang Pusat.

